definition.value: A secondary carboxamide resulting from the formal condensation of the of the carboxy group of 2-hydroxybenzoic acid with the primary amino group of (4S,5S)-4-amino-2-[2-(1H-imidazol-4-yl)ethyl]-5-methyl-1,2-oxazolidin-3-one. It is a siderophore isolated from Pseudomonas fluorescens AH2.
